snippet.title: DRAGON BALL Z: KAKAROT — "BARDOCK - Alone Against Fate" Battle for Planet Vegeta Trailer
snippet.description:
Season Pass 2 for DRAGON BALL Z: KAKAROT is almost here! 

The time to fight for it all begins January 13th, 2023 in "BARDOCK - Alone Against Fate" - will you be ready to defend the Saiyans? 

If you play on next-gen, you can also join in too! 
https://www.bandainamcoent.com/games/dragon-ball-z-kakarot
